{"pageProps":{"post":{"id":"574","date":"2019. 9. 19. 21:47","title":"문경의 아름다움","content":"<p>(이제야 정리하는 추석 산책)</p>\n<p>추석에 정말 오랜만에 시골이라 할 수 있는 곳에 다녀왔다. 부모님이 여행을 가시는 바람에 시댁 -&gt; 처가의 방문 순서를 따를 필요가 없게 되어 처가의 할아버지가 계신 상주를 방문하게 되었다. (아직 처가는 할아버지가 살아계셔서 장인어른의 형제가 모두 모인다) 꽉 막힌 도로 때문에 너무너무 짜증 나긴 했지만 그래도 오랜만에 본 우리나라 자연의 아름다움을 한껏 느낄 수 있어서 참 좋았다.</p>\n<p>상주도 물론 아름다웠지만 오며가며 지나는 길에 들른 문경이 정말 아름다웠다. 내가 방문한 곳은 진남휴게소다.</p>\n<p><iframe mapdata=\"addr=%EA%B2%BD%EC%83%81%EB%B6%81%EB%8F%84%20%EB%AC%B8%EA%B2%BD%EC%8B%9C%20%EB%A7%88%EC%84%B1%EB%A9%B4&amp;addtype=1&amp;confirmid=&amp;docid=&amp;idx=1&amp;ifrH=362px&amp;ifrW=490px&amp;mapHeight=362&amp;mapInfo=%7B%22version%22%3A2%2C%22mapWidth%22%3A490%2C%22mapHeight%22%3A362%2C%22mapCenterX%22%3A751810%2C%22mapCenterY%22%3A879723%2C%22mapLevel%22%3A4%2C%22coordinate%22%3A%22wcongnamul%22%2C%22markInfo%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22graphicInfo%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22roadviewInfo%22%3A%5B%5D%7D&amp;mapWidth=490&amp;mapX=751810&amp;mapY=879723&amp;map_hybrid=false&amp;map_level=4&amp;map_type=TYPE_MAP&amp;rcode=4728036000&amp;tel=&amp;title=\" src=\"/proxy/plusmapViewer.php?id=maps_1568884997142\" id=\"maps_1568884997142\" width=\"540px\" height=\"350px\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" data-ke-type=\"map\" data-maps-data=\"addr=%EA%B2%BD%EC%83%81%EB%B6%81%EB%8F%84%20%EB%AC%B8%EA%B2%BD%EC%8B%9C%20%EB%A7%88%EC%84%B1%EB%A9%B4&amp;addtype=1&amp;confirmid=&amp;docid=&amp;idx=1&amp;ifrH=362px&amp;ifrW=490px&amp;mapHeight=362&amp;mapInfo=%7B%22version%22%3A2%2C%22mapWidth%22%3A490%2C%22mapHeight%22%3A362%2C%22mapCenterX%22%3A751810%2C%22mapCenterY%22%3A879723%2C%22mapLevel%22%3A4%2C%22coordinate%22%3A%22wcongnamul%22%2C%22markInfo%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22graphicInfo%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22roadviewInfo%22%3A%5B%5D%7D&amp;mapWidth=490&amp;mapX=751810&amp;mapY=879723&amp;map_hybrid=false&amp;map_level=4&amp;map_type=TYPE_MAP&amp;rcode=4728036000&amp;tel=&amp;title=\" data-maps-mapx=\"879723\" data-maps-mapy=\"879723\" data-maps-thumbnail=\"https://ssl.daumcdn.net/map3/staticmap/image?center=751810%2C879723&amp;lv=4&amp;size=540x350&amp;srs=WCONGNAMUL&amp;\"></iframe></p>\n<p>진남휴게소는 굽이굽이 흐르는 영강과 조령천이 만나는 곳에 있다. 이 곳에서는 가장 먼저 아름다운 풍광을 만날 수 있다. 굽이굽이 흐르는 영강과 폭포, 고모산성, 석현성이 어우러져 너무너무 아름다웠다.</p>\n<p><figure class='imagegridblock'><div class='image-container'><span data-url=\"https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/cLD1aL/btqymLYxSou/caSbwYBatHChSkXpWtVDg0/img.jpg\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\" style=\"width: 20.9196%;\" width=\"732\" height=\"976\"><img src='https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/cLD1aL/btqymLYxSou/caSbwYBatHChSkXpWtVDg0/img.jpg' srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.kakaocdn.net%2Fdn%2FcLD1aL%2FbtqymLYxSou%2FcaSbwYBatHChSkXpWtVDg0%2Fimg.jpg\" ></span><span data-url=\"https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/VItbz/btqymT9SUlY/LalBgrEOqvpfVyDhLQou2k/img.jpg\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\" style=\"width: 37.2146%;\" width=\"1302\" height=\"976\"><img src='https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/VItbz/btqymT9SUlY/LalBgrEOqvpfVyDhLQou2k/img.jpg' srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.kakaocdn.net%2Fdn%2FVItbz%2FbtqymT9SUlY%2FLalBgrEOqvpfVyDhLQou2k%2Fimg.jpg\" ></span><span data-url=\"https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/bG552a/btqyoPlaets/jgRAHViShkKWT7wXEBoXO1/img.jpg\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\" style=\"width: 37.2146%;\" width=\"1302\" height=\"976\"><img src='https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/bG552a/btqyoPlaets/jgRAHViShkKWT7wXEBoXO1/img.jpg' srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&fname=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.kakaocdn.net%2Fdn%2FbG552a%2FbtqyoPlaets%2FjgRAHViShkKWT7wXEBoXO1%2Fimg.jpg\" ></span></div></figure><figure class='imagegridblock'><div class='image-container'><span data-url=\"https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/1vNti/btqyp1rDZbr/UaKXRMLe8kVx6Mvtdu0kCk/img.jpg\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox\" style=\"width: 37.2146%;\" width=\"1302\" height=\"976\"><img src='https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/1vNti/btqyp1rDZbr/UaKXRMLe8kVx6Mvtdu0kCk/img.jpg' srcset=\"https://img1.daumcdn.net/